      "requiredLevel": 5,
      "achievedLevel": 3,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Quantitative validation metric (e.g., E_avg) computed with full uncertainty propagation; model inadequacy formally characterised.",
      "rationale": "Predicted hemolysis index compared to bench data; mean error is 22%, exceeding the 15% acceptance threshold. Uncertainty propagation performed via Monte Carlo but model inadequacy term not formally separated from experimental uncertainty, preventing achievement of required level 5."
    },
    {
