      "acceptanceCriteria": "QoIs directly map to the clinical decision metric (plasma-free hemoglobin index); sensitivity analysis demonstrates QoI dominance.",
      "rationale": "Plasma-free hemoglobin index is used as primary QoI and is clinically relevant, but a formal sensitivity analysis linking simulation outputs to the regulatory decision threshold has not been documented, limiting achieved level to 3."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
