      "acceptanceCriteria": "Validation activities performed at operating conditions overlapping the intended VAD envelope; geometric similarity confirmed.",
      "rationale": "Validation conducted on the FDA generic pump geometry at 5 L/min; however, the intended VAD operating envelope extends to 6 L/min and the validation dataset does not cover this upper bound, reducing achieved level by one gradation."
