      "rationale": "Only the Giersiepen-Wurzinger power-law hemolysis model was used. No alternative model forms were evaluated and no Bayesian model selection was performed. Flagged as a critical epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
