      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Sufficient replicate experiments to characterise inter-sample variability; statistical power analysis documented.",
      "rationale": "Bench hemolysis measurements from a single experimental campaign with n=3 replicates. Statistical power analysis not performed; inter-sample variability is not fully characterised. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5."
    },
    {
